lead_paragraph: Tokyo Olympic organizers agreed Wednesday to hold some of the baseball and softball competition of the 2020 Games in Fukushima, the region devastated by the 2011 earthquake, tsunami and nuclear disaster.

headline.print_headline: Fukushima to Host Some Baseball, Softball Games at '20 Games
